QuestData.Title: Thaldraszsus
QuestData.Description:
Alexstrasza the Life-Binder is arranging a meeting of the Seat of the Aspects to discuss the threat of the Primalists.
She has put out a call for any willing adventurers to come help.
QuestData.LogDescription: Travel to Valdrakken and meet with Alexstrasza the Life-Binder.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Travel to Valdrakken and meet with Alexstrasza the Life-Binder.
